::GoldenEye::

She flies off away from the battle field and flies to the forest.  
She swoops down and lands on a tree branch.  She sees something 
moving in the bushes below.  It kind of looks like a big mouse or 
rat.  It's deep in the bushes and she can't make it out that well.  
She flys over and perches about the creature.  It a bot.  A rat bot.  
She looks at it for a moment.  She smiles,"Hello there."
